# --- Captioning + planning (Anthropic) --------------------------------------
# Server-side only, never exposed to the browser. With NO key set, /api/caption
# and /api/plan fall back to deterministic local heuristics so the
# drop → caption → make → preview loop still works offline.
#
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- Rendering --------------------------------------------------------------
# Where the /api/render proxy forwards to the stateless MP4 render worker
# (npm run worker). The worker stays on the internal network; only this proxy
# is same-origin. Defaults to the local worker on :3172.
# RENDER_WORKER_URL=http://localhost:3172

# --- Pod --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Pod base URL. Defaults to the shared mind-node on :3011 (see SOLID-SERVER.md).
NEXT_PUBLIC_POD_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3011/

# OIDC issuer. Defaults to POD_BASE_URL when unset (see src/lib/solid/session.ts).
# In production every sibling points at https://pods.mindpods.org/ for SSO.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SOLID_ISSUER=http://localhost:3011/
